snippet.title: Assetto Corsa Competizione - E3 Tech Demo Gameplay 3/4 - Day&Night Cycle
snippet.description:
With E3 Expo in full swing, we're proud to be able to showcase gameplay footage of Assetto Corsa Competizione with our community for the very first time! 
Our team are working absolutely flat out behind the scenes on the upcoming Official BLANCPAIN GT SERIES title, so we hope you like what you see! Let us know in the comments below...
At E3? Be sure to head on over to the Thrustmaster booth this week and give #ACCompetizione a try! What's more, set the quickest lap time to win a racing cockpit. Head over to the South Hall and speak to a member of the team for more information.
